carin-rtpbc-expanded-coverage-class-value-set


Defining URL:http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin/ValueSet/rtpbc-expanded-coverage-class
Version:0.1.11
Name:CARINRTPBCExpandedCoverageClassValueSet
Definition:

This value set adds concepts to the HL7-maintained coverage class value set related to discount coupons.

Publisher:CARIN Alliance
Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle


The additional coverage class values contained in a code system included in this value set (http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin/CodeSystem/rtpbc-coupon-coverage-class) could potentially be added to the respective HL7/FHIR coverage-class code system and value set prior to publication of this guide.



Used in...

  • CARIN RTPBC Request Coverage Identifiers
